{"serial": "14014", "department_serial": 16, "code": "PD7255", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Classics of Chinese Philosophy", "ch": "中國哲學經典"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Chung-Hsiu"], "ch": ["黃崇修"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "439"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 20, "department": {"ch": "哲學研究所碩士班", "en": "Master of Philosophy"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 2, "selected": 11, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程目標主要希望透過《近思錄》之經典導讀及討論，以引導同學對於北宋四子諸如周敦頤、張載、程顥、程頤等儒者之論點有深一層之思想掌握，進而在此有機性的思想展開下，幫助同學對於宋明理學之整體思維結構有一清楚而真確之理解。", "en": "“The main purpose of this course is to guide and discuss the classic of the Book of Jin Si Lu.Let students to have a deep understaning of the argument of the four theorists Zhou Dunyi, Chen Hao, Chen Yi and Zhang Zai in North Song Dynasty.Further, under this organic idea to help stundents have a clear and true understanding of the overall thinking structure of Neo-Confucianism of Song and Ming Dynasties.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程將依天道、心性、工夫三種視角，以歷史發展之步驟分別討論北宋四子的天道思想發展成心性論架構之後，最後如何形成一套其自身之工夫實踐系統。在每一次的系列討論之後，開放多元討論北宋四子理論之優缺及發展軌跡。", "en": "“This course will be based on the three perspectives: the Way of Heaven, Human Nature and Self-cultivation.Taking the steps of historical development, we discuss separately the development of the Way of Heaven to the Theories of Human Nature in the four theorists of North Song Dynasty.And finally, form a Self-cultivation system of its own.After each series of discussions.Open multivariate discussion of the advantages, disadvantages and development trajectory of the four theorists of North Song Dynasty.“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“教科書/參考書：\n朱熹·呂祖謙編《近思錄》\n陳榮捷《近思錄詳註集評》(台北：台灣學生書局，1992年)“", "en": "“The Book of Jin Si Lu was edited by Zhu Xi and Lu Zuqian.\nChen,Jung-Chieh《Detailed commentary of Jin Si Lu》(Taipei：Student Book Co., Ltd.，1992)“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "研討", "en": ["Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席率30％ 課堂討論30％ 期末報告40％", "en": "Attendance rate 30％ Classroom discussion 30％ Final report 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期三下午十二點至二點", "en": "\"Wednesday, 12:00PM-1400PM\""}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "中國哲學現代詮釋課程群", "en": "中國哲學現代詮釋課程群"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "理論觀念", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "批判創造", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "研究教學", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "學理應用", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際互動", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "ability to appreciate ideas and theories", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to think critically and creatively", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "ability to undertake research and teaching", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to apply theory to real world", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "ability to appreciate arts and humanities", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to conduct international exchanges", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["系所:限哲學研究所碩士班、哲學研究所博士班。", "學制:限碩士班、博士班。", "學制:限學士班。年級:限三年級、四年級。"], "en": ["Depar